{{greeting}}
Dear {{memberName}},

We would like to inform you that your invoice for the upcoming billing period has been generated and is now available for review.

To ensure uninterrupted access to your workspace and services, please settle the outstanding balance on or before the due date. You can view the detailed breakdown and make a secure payment via the OFIS SQUARE Mobile App or our Web Portal.

Invoice Number: {{invoiceNumber}}
Due Date: {{dueDate}}
Amount Due: {{amount}}

Thank you for being a valued member.

{{greeting}}
Dear {{memberName}},

Thank you for reaching out to us.

We would like to confirm that your support request has been successfully received and logged in our system with the following details:

Ticket ID: {{id}}
Category: {{Category}}

Our team is currently reviewing your request and will take the necessary action to resolve it at the earliest. You can expect an update from us shortly.

If you have any additional information that may help us address your concern faster, please reply to this email and mention your Ticket ID for reference.

We appreciate your patience and thank you for choosing OFIS SQUARE.

Dear {{memberName}},

Your reservation for a meeting space has been successfully processed. We have reserved the following slot for your upcoming session:

Meeting Room: {{meetingRoom}}
Location: {{building}}
Time Slot: {{timeSlot}}

Important Information:
Access: You can manage your booking via the App or Web Portal.
Check-in: Please ensure you check into the room via the app or tablet to avoid automatic cancellation.

Dear {{memberName}},

This is a courtesy reminder regarding your scheduled meeting room reservation today at OFIS SQUARE. 

Meeting Room: {{meetingRoom}}
Location: {{building}}
Time Slot: {{timeSlot}}

To ensure a seamless experience, please arrive a few minutes early and check in directly through the OFIS SQUARE Mobile App.

Regards,
Team OFIS SQUARE

Dear {{greeting}},

Your payment has been successfully processed.

Service Details:
- Service Type: {{serviceType}}
- Service Name: {{serviceName}}
- Building: {{buildingName}}
- Date: {{serviceDate}}
- Time Slot: {{timeSlot}}

Payment Details:
- Amount Paid: ₹{{amount}}
- Payment Mode: {{paymentMode}}
- Transaction ID: {{transactionId}}
- Invoice Number: {{invoiceNumber}}
- Payment Date: {{paymentDate}}

Thank you for choosing Ofis Square. We look forward to serving you.

Regards,
Team Ofis Square

Dear {{memberName}},

Thank you for your RSVP! We are pleased to confirm your registration for our upcoming event, {{eventName}}.

Event: {{eventName}}
Date: {{eventDate}}
Location: {{building}}

Please have your App ready upon arrival to check in. See you soon!

Best regards,
Community Team OFIS SQUARE

{{greeting}}
Dear Community Team,

A new support ticket has been raised by {{memberName}} from {{buildingName}}.

Ticket Details:
ID: {{ticketId}}
Category: {{Category}}
Priority: {{priority}}
Description: {{description}}

You can view and manage this ticket here: {{ctaLink}}

Best regards,
OFIS SQUARE System

{{greeting}}
Dear Team Member,

A support ticket has been assigned/reassigned to you.

Ticket Details:
ID: {{ticketId}}
Building: {{buildingName}}
Category: {{category}}
Priority: {{priority}}
Member/Client: {{memberName}}

Description:
{{description}}

Please take the necessary action. View details here: {{ctaLink}}

Best regards,
OFIS SQUARE Support

Dear {{memberName}},

A visitor has been scheduled to meet you at OFIS SQUARE.

Visitor Details:
Name: {{visitorName}}
Company: {{visitorCompany}}
Purpose: {{purpose}}

Visit Details:
Building: {{buildingName}}
Date: {{visitDate}}
Time: {{visitTime}}

Please ensure you are available at the scheduled time.

You will be notified again once the visitor arrives at reception.

Regards,
Team OFIS SQUARE

A draft payment has been submitted and requires finance verification.

Client Details:
Company Name: {{companyName}}
Client Name: {{clientName}}
Building: {{buildingName}}

Payment Details:
Invoice Number: {{invoiceNumber}}
Amount: ₹{{amount}}
Payment Mode: {{paymentMode}}
Transaction Reference: {{transactionReference}}
Submission Date: {{submittedDate}}

Please review the submitted payment proof and approve or reject it from the OFIS SQUARE platform.

Regards,
OFIS SQUARE System

Dear {{clientName}},

A new Pro Forma Invoice for {{companyName}} at {{buildingName}} has been generated for the billing period {{billingPeriod}}.

Details:
Pro Forma Number: {{proformaNumber}}
Total Amount: ₹{{totalAmount}}
Due Date: {{dueDate}}
Generated Date: {{generatedDate}}

Please review and approve the same via the OFIS SQUARE platform.

Best regards,
System OFIS SQUARE

Dear {{clientName}},

Please find attached the Pro Forma Invoice for your upcoming billing period at {{buildingName}}.

Summary:
Company: {{companyName}}
Amount: ₹{{totalAmount}}
Due Date: {{dueDate}}

You can also view and pay this online via the OFIS SQUARE app or portal.

Best regards,
Team OFIS SQUARE

Dear Admin,

The monthly invoice pipeline has completed a batch operation.

Operation Type: {{type}}
Total Successful: {{count}}
Total Errors: {{errorCount}}

Summary Table:
{{summaryTable}}

Best regards,
OFIS SQUARE System

{{greeting}}

New Comment on Contract #{{contractIdShort}}

Client: {{companyName}}
Status: {{status}}
Added by: {{addedBy}}

Comment: {{comment}}

View the full contract details in your dashboard.

{{greeting}}

Great news! The contract #{{contractIdShort}} for {{companyName}} has been approved by admin.

Status: {{status}}
Approved At: {{approvedAt}}

Next Steps:
- Send contract to client for review
- Await client approval
- Generate stamp paper after client approval

{{greeting}}

Your workspace contract is ready for your review and approval.

Contract Details:
Building: {{building}}
Capacity: {{peopleCount}} people
Monthly Rent: ₹{{monthlyRent}}
Contract Period: {{startDate}} - {{endDate}}

To review and approve:
1. Login to {{portalLink}}
2. Navigate to the Contracts section
3. Review and approve or provide feedback

Thank you,
Ofis Square Team

{{greeting}}

The contract for {{companyName}} has been sent for digital signature via Zoho Sign.

Contract Details:
Contract ID: #{{contractIdShort}}
Building: {{building}}
Status: Awaiting Client Signature
Sent At: {{sentAt}}

Next Steps:
- Client will receive an email from Zoho Sign
- Client will review and sign the document digitally
- You will be notified once the contract is signed

{{greeting}}

Congratulations! The contract for {{companyName}} has been digitally signed and is now active.

Contract Details:
Contract ID: #{{contractIdShort}}
Building: {{building}}
Status: Signed & Active
Signed At: {{signedAt}}

Next Steps:
- Client onboarding can proceed
- Workspace allocation can be finalized
- Invoicing can be initiated
